title: R-Ladies Jakarta 5th Meetup: Classical tests with R!
description:
We're having out fifth meetup, real soon!

Saturday, 30th November 2019 from 14.00-17.00 WIB, at Mozilla Community Space Jakarta, Jl. Kuningan Bar. 1 No.26, Mampang Prapatan, DKI Jakarta 12710

Are you still confused about parametric and non-parametric tests? Assumption of normality, etc? This is the time to be enlightened!! Hahahaha...

We will learn about the parametric (t-test, ANOVA, ANCOVA) and non-parametric tests (Wilcoxon, Kruskal Wallis), then Chi-squared and correlation tests, and how to run the analysis in R.

Some IMPORTANT stuff:
1. Our current space can have maximum 25 persons, so hurry up reserve your spot!
2. Check previous meetups docs here: https://github.com/RLadiesJakarta
3. E-mail us at jakarta@rladies.org or tweet to "@rladiesjakarta" for any inquiries regarding this event!
4. Don't forget to have RStudio readily installed in your computer
5. VERY IMPORTANT: If you're very new to R, we need you to go through these two documents BEFORE the meetup:
1. Intro to R.pdf
2. Starter Kit R.pdf
You can download and read the descriptions here: https://github.com/RLadiesJakarta/starter-kit

title: R-Ladies Jakarta 4th Meetup: Visualization
description:
We're having out fourth meetup, real soon!

Saturday, 26th October 2019 from 14.00-17.00 WIB, at Mozilla Community Space Jakarta, Jl. Kuningan Bar. 1 No.26, Mampang Prapatan, DKI Jakarta 12710

This time we will be venturing into visualization with R using base R and ggplot2. So get ready to create pretty plots!

Don't forget to bring your own laptop and have R software already installed in your computers, and do email us to let us know if this is your first time using R so we can have a short introductory session.

This meetup is a free entrance, thanks to the support of Komunitas Mozilla Indonesia for providing the place & WCS-Indonesia for providing us some snacks. But you are more than welcomed to bring some snacks and drinks to share with the other attendees!

To make this mini workshop comfortable for all attendees, we're limiting the number of attendance up to 25 people, so hurry book your spot!

E-mail us at "jakarta@rladies.org" or tweet to "@rladiesjakarta" (https://twitter.com/RLadiesJakarta) for any inquiries regarding this event!

title: R-Ladies Jakarta Second Meetup: R ABSOLUTE BEGINNER!
description:
Second Jakarta R-Ladies meetup is coming soon!

For our second meetup, let's start with R absolute beginner mini workshop. Sunday, August 25, 2019 from 09.00-12.00 WIB, at Multipurpose room - Gedung Seameo Recfon. Kompleks UI Salemba, Jln Salemba Raya no 6, Jakarta Pusat.

We will start with a brief introduction of R, followed by basics on how to use R, and if we have some time left, we'll discuss a bit about some descriptive statistics. Don't forget to bring your own laptop and install R software in your computers.

title: R-Ladies Jakarta First Meetup
description:
First Jakarta R-Ladies meetup is coming soon!

R-Ladies is a worldwide organization whose mission is to promote gender diversity in the R community. So, if you want to get to know R better, come join us at Kudoplex Auditorium on 28th of July 2019 from 9 AM to 12 AM to discuss our favorite statistical programming language! We will first introduce the R-Ladies Global initiative and then proceed to discuss general knowledge on how to use R and some of its functions.

To increase the better experience for each of the attendees, we're limiting our meet up to 50 persons, so sign up quickly before your spot is taken.

This meetup is a free entrance, and we'll prepare some snacks, thanks to the support of Grab Kudo for providing us a comfortable place to gather. But you still need to bring your own laptop (BYOL).
If you intend to come, please fill our survey to help us prepare for the event: https://forms.gle/Qvqo4ixh4K467jjv7

E-mail us at "jakarta@rladies.org" or tweet to "@rladiesjakarta" (https://twitter.com/RLadiesJakarta) for any inquiries regarding this event!

Sunday, 2nd February 2020 from 14.00-17.00 WIB, at Mozilla Community Space Jakarta, Jl. Kuningan Bar. 1 No.26, Mampang Prapatan, DKI Jakarta 12710

We will have a refreshing topic as we commence our yearlong R-Ladies series of meet-ups, and what better way to start through learning Shiny apps in R with our always awesome Erika Siregar? So, hurry and join us!
